            "id": 6069747,
            "title": "《大手成交》阿里一手27萬股非自動對盤,涉資3092萬元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社18日專訊》阿里(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09988:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09988\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09988-HK</a>)於2:23pm錄得1手27萬股非自動對盤,每股造114.5元,較上日收市價高1.8%,涉資3092萬元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　阿里現價升2.3%,報115.1元;成交5685萬股,成交金額65.61億元,主動買沽比率50:50,資金淨主動賣出1500萬元。(rw)</p></section><section><p class=\"\"></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main>",
