            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社18日專訊》寧德時代(03750-HK)曾升近6%,最高價見395.4元,創上市新高,現升5.7%,報395.2元,最低價380.2元;成交184.05萬股,成交金額7.12億元;主動買沽比率60:40,資金淨主動買入1.34億元。現時最大淨被動買入券商為花旗環球金融亞洲,金額4657萬元,加權平均成交價386.324元;現時最大淨被動賣出券商為富途證券國際,金額4395萬元,加權平均成交價387.403元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　基本資料</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　　　　　====</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>現價</td><td>395.200</td><td>變動</td><td>+5.67%</td></tr><tr><td>最高價</td><td>395.400</td><td>最低價</td><td>380.200</td></tr><tr><td>成交股數</td><td>184.05萬股</td><td>成交金額</td><td>7.12億</td></tr><tr><td>10天平均</td><td>375.360</td><td>歷史波幅%</td><td>36.668</td></tr><tr><td>20天平均</td><td>349.390</td><td>加權平均價</td><td>386.862</td></tr><tr><td>50天平均</td><td>-</td><td>RSI14</td><td>76.373</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　股份狀態:創上市新高;主動買沽比率60:40,資金淨主動買入1.34億元</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>寧德時代(03750-HK)</td><td>395.20</td><td>+5.67</td></tr><tr><td>布魯可(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00325:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00325\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00325-HK</a>)</td><td>128.80</td><td>-1.38</td></tr><tr><td>恒瑞醫藥(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01276:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01276\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01276-HK</a>)</td><td>73.45</td><td>+2.44</td></tr><tr><td>古茗(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01364:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01364\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01364-HK</a>)</td><td>24.55</td><td>-2.39</td></tr><tr><td>蜜雪集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02097:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02097\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02097-HK</a>)</td><td>500.00</td><td>-0.50</td></tr><tr><td>海天味業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:03288:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/03288\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">03288-HK</a>)</td><td>36.05</td><td>+1.55</td></tr><tr><td>周六福(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06168:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06168\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06168-HK</a>)</td><td>40.35</td><td>-1.71</td></tr><tr><td>IFBH(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06603:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06603\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06603-HK</a>)</td><td>39.65</td><td>-2.58</td></tr><tr><td>赤峰<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/XAUUSDOZ\">黃金</a>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06693:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Artic